Description: SCIBED (Single-Cell Imputation Benchmarking of Epigenomic Data) is an R package designed to evaluate the performance of imputation algorithms for single-cell epigenomic data. It enables users to generate in silico epigenomic datasets with controlled levels of data quality and provides tools to assess the output of imputation methods quantitatively.
